{"tid":1326660,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真人真事","createTime":"2019-07-17T10:02:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T10:02:00.000Z","uid":168922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d91ed9ce08e17e70ba48637104ca40a45919ed21","tid":1326660,"uid":168922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T10:02:00.000Z","msg":"工作關係呢排接觸多左大陸人，返工好悶唯有不停R水吹<br />\n有個大陸西帶埋個10歲女日日上來講遊行人士收錢又點又盛，我靜雞雞問佢個女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：妹妹你支唔支持共產黨呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：支持呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你愛唔愛中國呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：愛呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咁你係咩人呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：點解你愛中國又支持共產黨但係話自己係香港人既？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：因為香港好玩<br />\n<br />\n之後我開youtube畀左條片佢睇<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cfPel4PVsow\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcfPel4PVsow&d=SosmRuku1xQpFtIKZJ5aucg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=180a1b8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cfPel4PVsow</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：妹妹你睇到啲咩？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：&amp;#__#+#）$-$-#-#+_-#+警察打人呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：點解啲哥哥姐姐要畀警察打？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />： ？_？ ？_？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：因為佢地對抗共產黨，所以政府就派警察來打佢地，唔畀哥哥姐姐反對中國<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我同你講祕密，其實我爸爸媽媽都唔鍾意共產黨嫁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我哥哥（21歲讀廣州大學）佢係大陸反對共產黨畀警察捉左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}